<!DOCTYPE html>
<html tal:omit-tag="textual">
<head tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <title tal:omit-tag="textual">Change in the Status of Your Application</title>
</head>
<body tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <h1 tal:omit-tag="textual">Evolution of Your Application</h1>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Hello <span tal:replace="user" tal:condition="exists:user" tal:omit-tag="textual">Applicant's Name</span>,</p>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual tal:omit-tag="textual"">Your application on the platform <span tal:replace="site_url">URL</span> as a <span tal:replace="python:candidature.type">Role</span>
        <span tal:condition="python:candidature.state == CandidatureStates.APPROVED">has been accepted</span>
        <span tal:condition="python:candidature.state == CandidatureStates.REFUSED">has been rejected</span>
        <span tal:condition="python:candidature.state not in [CandidatureStates.APPROVED, CandidatureStates.REFUSED]">is under processing and has changed its status</span>
        .
    </p>
    
    <p  tal:omit-tag="textual">Here are the details of its evolution:</p>
    <ul tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <li tal:omit-tag="textual">Candidature ID: <span tal:replace="python:candidature.oid">Application ID</span></li>
        <li tal:omit-tag="textual">Transition Date: <span tal:replace="python:candidature.modifications[-1]">Last transition</span></li>
        <li tal:omit-tag="textual">New Status: <span tal:replace="python:candidature.state">New application status</span></li>
    </ul>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for your participation.</p>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Best regards,</p>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">The team of <span tal:replace="site_name">Site Name</span></p>
</body>
</html>
